This project is a Vim configuration Python and Django dedicated.
Add modules for coffeescript, stylus and jade.

Installation:

    git clone git@github.com:frankrousseau/dotvim.git ~/.vim


Create symlink:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc


Install packages:

    sudo aptitude install git pep8 exuberant-ctags python-rope 


Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule sync
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    git submodule foreach git submodule init
    git submodule foreach git submodule update
    
    
Fork from : git://github.com/tcolombo/dotvim.git
